## Admin Credentials

Your admin username is **{{adminUsername}}**. Set your password during the first login
for each service that requires it.

## Remaining Manual Steps

1. Open Jellyseerr at the URL above and complete the initial setup wizard.
2. Connect Jellyseerr to your Jellyfin server.
3. Request a movie or TV show to verify the full pipeline is working.
4. In Prowlarr, add your preferred indexers and sync them to Sonarr and Radarr.
5. In qBittorrent, verify the download categories match what Sonarr and Radarr expect.
